fields.title: Vivid Dream
fields.description: I had a dream where I was flying over a beautiful landscape.

fields.title: Nightmare
fields.description: It was a terrifying dream about being chased by a monster.

fields.title: Lucid Dream
fields.description: I was aware that I was dreaming and could control the dream environment.

fields.title: Recurring Dream
fields.description: It was the same dream I've been having for weeks, where I'm lost in a maze.

fields.title: Prophetic Dream
fields.description: I had a dream that seemed to predict a future event.
